      "x": 416,
      "y": 116,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 128,
      "text": "QUERY (RFC 10008)\n✅ Safe · ✅ Idempotent\n✅ Request body\n✅ CDN cacheable\n(body-aware cache key)\nTHE MISSING MIDDLE",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
